  ('dietitian-moex-10756', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '對於一個體重過重但尚未達預期成人體重的小孩，其體重控制的目標是：', '["每週減重1公斤", "每週減重2公斤", "維持現在體重或緩慢的增重", "不作任何處理直到體重達預期成人體重"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3e329c29ee43", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094130", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
